    "title": "Senior Plant Manager at Greaves Cotton",
    "description": "Are you a skilled Plant Manager looking for your next big career move? Greaves Cotton in Surat offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Greaves Cotton:\nGreaves Cotton is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n• Maintain accurate production records and prepare daily reports\n• Implement lean manufacturing and continuous improvement initiatives\n• Manage raw material procurement and inventory levels\n• Conduct root cause analysis for quality rejections and defects\n• Manage supplier quality audits and vendor development\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in GD&T\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in SolidWorks\n• Proficiency in Kaizen\n• Proficiency in Root Cause Analysis\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in Lean Manufacturing\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Surat, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Greaves Cotton!",
